You will ask if I'm ok,
I will say I'm fine,
and you will stay quiet,
knowing I'm ok,
but I'm not ok, I always say I am,
because no one will ever understand why,
I will say it every time you ask me, 
but I will always lie to you,
and then you'll stop asking because 
you know my answer.
And when I say the truth, you will ask,
why, and that is the problem, 
stop asking why, just listen,
I dont want to be questioned on how I feel,
because when you do,
I will ask myself the same question,
and I will not know the answer.
I will think so hard about it,
and eventually it will be too much to handle,
and before you know it, I'll end it.